metadata.name: Nouns Checkfy+ ⌐◨-◨ #1
metadata.description: ⌐◨-◨ Nouns Checkfy+ is a meme and non-fungible generative token project on the Ethereum blockchain, pixel characters based on people, places and things. We created 432 Nouns using the background of another notable collection, the VV Checks. New Nouns are created every day, soon others will appear here too.
